==Martuthunira==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/puwa/}}
===Etymology===
From Proto-Ngayarda ''*puka'', from Proto-Pama-Nyungan ''*puka''.
===Nominal===
'''puwa'''

# [[rotten|Rotten]].
